# Files and folders excluded from the distributed plugin (WP.org SVN deploy
# via 10up/action-wordpress-plugin-deploy, and any `wp dist-archive` use).
#
# Patterns are ANCHORED (leading /) on purpose: an unanchored `src` would also
# strip build/**/src or any nested src/ and risk fataling the plugin.
#
# vendor/ does NOT ship — it holds dev tooling only (phpunit); the free build
# has no runtime composer deps and the Freemius SDK ships inside Mailyard Pro.
# build/ SHIPS (compiled admin app); readme.txt points to the GitHub repo for
# the unminified src/.

/.git
/.github
/.claude
/.wordpress.org
/node_modules
/src
/scripts
/tests
/bin
/docs
/vendor
/package.json
/package-lock.json
/composer.json
/composer.lock
/phpcs.xml
/phpcs.xml.dist
/phpunit.xml
/phpunit.xml.dist
/webpack.config.js
/tailwind.config.js
/postcss.config.js
/components.json
/.gitignore
/.editorconfig
/.distignore
/.eslintrc
/.eslintrc.js
/.eslintrc.json
/.prettierrc
/.prettierrc.js
/AGENTS.md
/CLAUDE.md
/STATUS.md
/*.zip
.DS_Store
